code: public static BlobPath cleanPath() {     return new BlobPath(). }
public String[] toArray() {     return paths.toArray(new String[paths.size()]). }
public BlobPath add(String path) {     List<String> paths = new ArrayList<>(this.paths).     paths.add(path).     return new BlobPath(Collections.unmodifiableList(paths)). }
public String buildAsString() {     String p = String.join(SEPARATOR, paths).     if (p.isEmpty() || p.endsWith(SEPARATOR)) {         return p.     }     return p + SEPARATOR. }
@Override public String toString() {     StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder().     for (String path : paths) {         sb.append('[').append(path).append(']').     }     return sb.toString(). }
